                    </div>

                    <div style="margin-top: 20px; border-top: 1px dashed #00ff00; padding-top: 15px;">
                        <h4 style="color: #ffff00; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.95em;">‚Ėļ WEEKLY MILESTONES</h4>
