                        <p>Engaging with peers and instructors to collectively explore digital humanities challenges.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="treasure">
                        <div class="treasure-header">‚öôÔłŹ Technical Skills</div>
                        <p>Proficiency with various digital tools and platforms for humanities research and creation.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="treasure">
